0:00:00.000,0:00:05.320
As Prophet T.B. Joshua was ministering prayer to the congregation at the Monday live prophetic service

0:00:05.320,0:00:10.020
in the name of Jesus Christ, a man cried out to him for his special attention.

0:00:10.020,0:00:11.620
I am a blasphemer.

0:00:11.620,0:00:12.800
Are you a pastor?

0:00:12.800,0:00:13.480
Yes, sir.

0:00:13.480,0:00:14.500
You are a blasphemer?

0:00:14.500,0:00:16.580
Yes, sir. I have a confession to make.

0:00:16.580,0:00:19.360
The confession is that we have been praying that God should take away your power.

0:00:19.360,0:00:22.840
We are PFN (Pentecostal Fellowship Nigeria) in Anambra State, Nigeria.

0:00:22.840,0:00:27.080
I came to meet you. I have never seen a pastor like you.

0:00:27.080,0:00:28.380
I have never seen your type.

0:00:28.380,0:00:30.840
Why were you people praying to take away my life?

0:00:30.840,0:00:32.580
We were seeing you as an anti-Christ.

0:00:32.580,0:00:36.600
And even that the Anointing Water was initiation into the marine world.

0:00:36.600,0:00:41.460
We said it was bewitching. The people were mesmerized; they'd just dance and fall

0:00:41.460,0:00:44.260
and that it was not real power from Heaven.

0:00:44.260,0:00:45.080
Why?

0:00:45.080,0:00:50.060
These are lies of the enemy. I have come here for forgiveness.

0:00:50.060,0:00:52.720
That's why I came so that it would be well with me.

0:00:52.720,0:00:53.720
So you are a pastor?

0:00:53.720,0:00:54.380
Yes, sir.

0:00:54.380,0:00:56.640
So, all the pastors in which state?

0:00:56.640,0:00:58.040
Anambra.

0:00:58.040,0:00:58.640
Yes, sir.

0:00:58.640,0:01:01.040
You people were praying that God should take away my life?

0:01:01.040,0:01:02.560
Yes, sir.

0:01:02.560,0:01:04.260
And humble you.

0:01:04.260,0:01:07.160
Okay, thank you. I want to see you, sir.

0:01:07.160,0:01:10.040
Go and wait for me.

0:01:10.040,0:01:13.560
Emmanuel! 
(God with us - Matthew 1:23)

0:01:13.560,0:01:17.480
I am Pastor Chidi Daniel;

0:01:17.480,0:01:23.460
a pastor with Grace of God Mission in Anambra State, Nigeria.

0:01:23.460,0:01:26.300
I also belong to the PFN (Pentecostal Fellowship Nigeria).

0:01:26.300,0:01:38.240
Based on the information from our superiors, those I highly esteemed, I was ruined.

0:01:38.240,0:01:41.060
That was the position.

0:01:41.060,0:01:52.460
I was appointed as music and crusade director and as such, I went around

0:01:52.460,0:01:56.640
saying what they told me to say - that was a fallacy -

0:01:56.640,0:02:08.320
that the man of God, Prophet T.B. Joshua, sleeps with snakes and lives in the water.

0:02:08.320,0:02:10.700
You can imagine...

0:02:10.700,0:02:17.300
And because of this, I went about telling people not to go to The SCOAN.

0:02:17.300,0:02:25.780
I said it was an anti-Christ church and "the synagogue of satan"

0:02:25.780,0:02:30.000
where nothing good can come out from.

0:02:30.000,0:02:35.840
Because I said these things, I didn't know I was ruining myself too.

0:02:35.840,0:02:40.400
The problems continued for me.

0:02:40.400,0:02:43.120
I didn't know where to turn to.

0:02:43.120,0:02:47.820
My children and family were ruined.

0:02:47.820,0:02:56.560
I lost my wife because of breast cancer, and my children died in an accident.

0:02:56.560,0:03:03.400
I got married to another woman but there was a problem. She left and went to her people.

0:03:03.400,0:03:07.680
The ministry was in shambles, and I didn't know what to do.

0:03:07.680,0:03:15.860
I asked myself, "What is wrong? I'm preaching the Gospel and it is a gateway to blessings.

0:03:15.860,0:03:18.780
Why is my case an exception?"

0:03:18.780,0:03:20.680
I was confused.

0:03:20.680,0:03:28.120
I went to visit one of my cousins who is a doctor, and I watched Emmanuel TV.

0:03:28.120,0:03:35.020
I saw miracles that looked incredible, and I wondered.

0:03:35.020,0:03:39.400
My cousin said that this was hypnosis, that they were being mesmerized

0:03:39.400,0:03:47.700
and that when they were dazed, they collapsed on the ground.

0:03:47.700,0:03:54.880
Then I saw the Anointing Water.

0:03:54.880,0:04:02.220
I saw healing, deliverance and all manner of miracles through the Anointing Water.

0:04:02.220,0:04:14.320
I said that this man was living in the water and that this was another dimension of initiating people too.

0:04:14.320,0:04:22.300
I refused to accept the miracles and the authenticity of the mercy of God to humanity.

0:04:22.300,0:04:30.300
I was always seeing the negative side and there were repercussions upon my life and ministry.

0:04:30.300,0:04:37.920
Other pastors who watched Emmanuel TV were always telling me

0:04:37.920,0:04:43.920
that the miracles were not real but stage-managed. You can't believe it.

0:04:43.920,0:04:52.480
Even on Monday after my confession, three pastors called me.

0:04:52.480,0:05:00.520
I know that these are people that have Emmanuel TV in their homes.

0:05:00.520,0:05:03.560
But they are like the 'old' pharisees who stand on the way,

0:05:03.560,0:05:07.280
not allowing people to enter into their miracles.

0:05:07.280,0:05:15.320
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:05:15.320,0:05:23.280
I have discovered that the appointment as a crusade director has amounted to disappointment

0:05:23.280,0:05:30.320
and has brought ruin. My body is sick. Nothing is working.

0:05:30.320,0:05:35.180
I asked another friend of mine who is a medical doctor.

0:05:35.180,0:05:43.960
He told me that I have a confession to make, that I used to speak evil against the man of God

0:05:43.960,0:05:49.260
and that the Bible says that sin against man can be forgiven

0:05:49.260,0:05:55.560
but sin against the Holy Spirit would never be forgiven.

0:05:55.560,0:06:00.320
I didn't have the courage to come to The SCOAN

0:06:00.320,0:06:05.300
after I had told people that nothing good can come out of this place.

0:06:05.300,0:06:08.960
It was a difficult situation for me.

0:06:08.960,0:06:15.040
I still went back to watch Emmanuel TV in another pastor's house.

0:06:15.040,0:06:24.400
Then I met another pastor who told me that I had wronged an authority in Christ.

0:06:24.400,0:06:30.520
I said, "I have never insulted any man of God. Who could it be that I have insulted?

0:06:30.520,0:06:38.200
T.B. Joshua of The SCOAN, do we call him a man of God?"

0:06:38.200,0:06:43.200
The pastor told me, "You have missed it. Are you the one who makes people men of God?

0:06:43.200,0:06:52.320
Prophet T.B. Joshua is the one who can deliver you. You must go to him for deliverance".

0:06:52.320,0:06:57.020
It wasn't easy for me to come; it was another mountain before me.

0:06:57.020,0:07:04.000
I had to summon up courage, and I came to The SCOAN.

0:07:04.000,0:07:06.000
I came on Monday.

0:07:06.000,0:07:13.460
The wise men came and attended to me. I thank God.

0:07:13.460,0:07:25.400
When finally the man in the Synagogue, the man anointed, the man of the now...

0:07:25.400,0:07:32.040
When Prophet T.B. Joshua appeared, he was very humble;

0:07:32.040,0:07:37.660
he didn't look like us who dressed to intimidate.

0:07:37.660,0:07:48.240
I saw what I had never seen among my fellow preachers and old founders who are bishops.

0:07:48.240,0:07:54.420
Prophet T.B. Joshua hugged me. He laughed. He took pictures with me. Oh, what a simplicity!

0:07:54.420,0:07:58.980
What a humility! What a compassion!

0:07:58.980,0:08:02.760
Somebody even asked him for his Bible and he gave it to him.

0:08:02.760,0:08:05.460
I said, "No, I have not seen this kind".

0:08:05.460,0:08:16.440
Something was saying within me, "If we can produce these types, there will be peace in Nigeria".

0:08:16.440,0:08:21.900
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:08:21.900,0:08:27.900
Since I came, I have seen it in another way;

0:08:27.900,0:08:31.500
I see the place as an institution in your life and your word.

0:08:31.500,0:08:37.460
No one can see you on the road and believe that you are a Holy Ghost machine!

0:08:37.460,0:08:45.360
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:08:45.360,0:08:52.440
I'm sorry, man of God. I have sinned against the Holy Ghost and the Anointed of God.

0:08:52.440,0:08:56.160
Please, have mercy on me.

0:08:56.160,0:08:59.100
He has been troubled for the past one week.

0:08:59.100,0:09:02.680
I think he has expressed his feelings.

0:09:02.680,0:09:09.820
My relationship with my Nigerian pastors, God is aware.

0:09:09.820,0:09:19.060
If my people had seen what is happening here clearly,

0:09:19.060,0:09:22.820
you people from other countries wouldn't have access to me.

0:09:22.820,0:09:26.360
Now God will begin to open that understanding.

0:09:26.360,0:09:29.820
You know, this is the church of all nations.

0:09:29.820,0:09:34.040
My country's position should not be more than half percent.

0:09:34.040,0:09:45.100
If they had seen and accepted me in the beginning, it would have disturbed my mission to the world.

0:09:45.100,0:09:47.760
It is the will of God.

0:09:47.760,0:09:51.900
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:09:51.900,0:09:59.160
If they had accepted me and seen me clearly, it would have disturbed my mission to the whole world.

0:09:59.160,0:10:05.260
This church would have become a Nigerian church and it is not only a Nigerian church.

0:10:05.260,0:10:07.560
God is aware.

0:10:07.560,0:10:18.460
What they have been doing from the beginning was never a sin - God is aware.

0:10:18.460,0:10:25.740
I repeat again. God decided to allow that to happen.

0:10:25.740,0:10:28.580
God can use any foolish thing.

0:10:28.580,0:10:35.580
He used that to keep me for the nations and the whole world.

